	<name>NexaOS Customize</name>
	<summary>Customize your NexaOS desktop appearance</summary>
	<description>
		<p>
			NexaOS Customize is a powerful tool for personalizing your NexaOS desktop environment. 
			Built by Nexus Foundation, it provides an intuitive interface for managing themes, 
			layouts, extensions, and visual effects.
		</p>
		<p>Features include:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Quick layout presets for desktop configuration</li>
			<li>Material You color theming support</li>
			<li>GNOME Shell extension management</li>
			<li>Visual effects controls (blur, wobbly windows, magic lamp, desktop cube)</li>
			<li>System tray and desktop icons management</li>
			<li>Background logo customization</li>
		</ul>
	</description>
